cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use PolicyShift, please cite this repository.
title: "PolicyShift: Continual Post-Training for Agents Operating Under Evolving Enterprise Policies"
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-07-20"
license: Apache-2.0
authors:
  - name: PolicyShift Contributors
abstract: >
  PolicyShift is a synthetic research environment and post-training study of how
  small tool-using language models adapt to evolving enterprise policies using
  SFT, distillation, DPO, and verifier-guided RL.
keywords:
  - continual learning
  - LLM post-training
  - tool use
  - policy compliance
  - preference optimization
